nodes.text: A security guard, recently hired by Cosinga Palpatine as of 65 BBY, was tasked with retrieving Palpatine from the Jafan III at Hanna City Starport. He was murdered by Palpatine along with everyone else onboard soon after the yacht entered hyperspace; his body was disposed of by agents of Hego Damask along with the others. He was known to be stern and wry in character.
